{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_01_02",
  "title": "白石沙季 2話 輝いていますか？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ hi‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "沙季、何か事務所に用事か？\n今日は外出して、直帰の予定だったろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you need something at the office‚ Saki?\nI thought you said you were going back to the dorms directly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.40521580396841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、用というほどのことでもないのですが\nその……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it wasn’t so much something that I needed…\nIt’s‚ er…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.575865793228152,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "……実は、宣材用の写真を見に来たんです\n今日届くと聞いていましたから気になって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I wanted to have a look at the promotional photos\nthat were supposed to arrive today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.222721385955815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "なんだ、そうだったのか。すぐ見せるよ\n宣材用写真は……えーと、確かこの辺りに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ I see. Sure‚ let me get them.\nPromo photos… Let me see… Where could it be…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.52876083167891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さん\nもしかして失くしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…{user}-san.\nYou didn’t lose them‚ did you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.64818443487854,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いや違うって。ちょっと手間取っているだけだ\nほらここに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ of course not‚ I just need to find them…\nHere.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.17340940940076,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "だから先日も整理整頓をと言ったじゃないですか\n……もう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I said you should organize.\nHonestly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.7916661066887,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（まだ何か言いたそうな沙季だったが）\n（宣材写真を見た途端、目の色が変わった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Saki looks like she is going to keep going‚)\n(but her expression changes when she sees the promo photos.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.10362486472499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.41319633167285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "素晴らしいです\nみんなキラキラ輝いてます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re amazing.\nEveryone’s shining brightly",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.42782216709157,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "私が幼い頃に憧れたアイドル達と同じくらい\n眩しく見えます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "like the idols I used to aspire to when I was little.\nIt almost makes me dizzy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.00945485484428,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、みんなの良い所が引き出されて輝いてる\n必ず注目されるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ they really brought out the best out of everyone.\nIt’ll definitely catch people’s attention.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.06841428243061,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "はい、必ず\n私も同じ気持ちです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Absolutely.\nI feel the same way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.17031882330775,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "……あの、{user}さん\nちょっとお聞きしたいのですが、よろしいでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey‚ {user}-san.\nCan I ask you something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.27399307070876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "この写真、みんな眩しいくらい輝いていますよね\n……私は、どうでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone looks so brilliant in the photos.\nBut…what about me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.41534257450944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、私の写真だってよく撮れていると思うんです\nさすがプロのカメラマンさんの仕事だと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can tell it’s a good photo‚\nthe work of a professional photographer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.3820092411761,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、アイドルとして通用するレベルなのか\nどうか……自分じゃ分からないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But am I at the standard that an idol should be?\nI’m just not sure what to think…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.24867590784288,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "沙季……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.87313792517868,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "私は、小さな頃からアイドルに憧れていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was my childhood dream to become an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.22313794902054,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルが好きだから、アイドルになりたいから……\nだから、高校最後の年に思い切って挑戦しました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I loved idols‚ and I wanted to become one of them.\nComing into the last year of high school‚ I decided to try to go for it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.63447581739321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルになった後も、自分に出来る限りの\n努力は欠かさなかったつもりです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After becoming an idol‚\nI’ve tried to work as hard as I could.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.83447581739316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、どれだけ努力をしていても……\n自分がしっかりアイドルをやれているのか分かりません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But no matter how hard I work‚\nI still don’t know whether I’m good enough as an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.33447581739316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "だから、教えて下さい\n――私は輝けていますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please‚ tell me.\nAm I shining?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.7995069812844,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ここ最近のライブや握手会を思い出してみるといい\nお客さん一人一人の顔はどうだった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Think back to the recentlives and handshake sessions.\nDo you remember the expression on the fans’ faces?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.8328403146177,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-ski019.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.25323592733437,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-ski020.m4a",
      "text": "……みんな、満面の笑みで楽しんでくれていました\nそう思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I think everyone\nhad a big smile on their face.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.319902594001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-ski021.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、まるで私が小さかった頃みたいにニコニコして\n……あ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe. Just like I was when I was little.\n…Oh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.94036235227708,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "きっと昔の沙季と同じだ。お客さん達の目には\n沙季が輝いて見えたんじゃないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re just like you when you were little.\nIn their eyes‚ you’re shining brightly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.3751191928771,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-ski022.m4a",
      "text": "そう、なんでしょうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you really think so?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.0682066002649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。お客さんの反応に嘘はないからな\n沙季もみんなも、輝いているよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. The reactions of the fans don’t lie.\nEveryone’s shining brightly‚ including you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.8164379397196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
